```

**Coverage Delta**: This test would exercise:
- Error handling path in `handleRegularExpressionResult()` (line 3393)
- Group state consistency when regex refresh fails (line 2368-2374)
- Epoch management when `maybeUpdateRegularExpressions()` returns REGEX_FAILED
- Proper fallback behavior instead of cascading failures
- Member heartbeat handling during metadata refresh failures

